\v 24 Nawe han Č Abhafarisaayo bhiigwir…® gayo, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúAraheebha amasambwa k Čbh Čnaja bhwa Bh…®…®riz…®bhuri,\f + \fr 12:24 \fk Bh…®…®riz…®bhuri \ft ni‚ÄĎriina …®r…®nd…® rya \fqa Sh…®taani.\f*  Čm Čk Čr Č wa amasambwa!‚ÄĚ 
