\c 13  
\s1 Ekerenjo chu umubhusuri wa zimbusur Č 
\r (Maaroko 4:1‚ÄĎ9; Ruuka 8:4‚ÄĎ8) 
\p  
\v 1 Urusik Č ruyoruyo, Y…®…®su akarwa munyumba yiyo, akaja kwikara rusiz Č w…® …®nyanza.  
\v 2 Riribhita ik Čr Č rya abhaat Č r…®kaaza, rikiibhiringa han Č Y…®…®su aar…®. Akasik…®ra mubhwat Č, akiikara, abhaat Č bhakabha bhiimiiriir…® rusiz Č w…® …®nyanza.  
\v 3 Y…®…®su akabhabh Č Čr…®ra amang ľana maaru kobherenjo. Akabhuga, ‚ÄúMwitegeerere! Umubhusuri akaja kubhusura imbusur Č yaaz…®.\fig Umubhusuri wi imbusur Č|alt="Msiaji wa mbegu" src="GT00046.tif" size="col" loc="MAT 13:3" copy="Gordon Thompson ¬© 2012 Wycliffe Bible Translators, Inc." ref="13:3" \fig* 
\v 4 Han Č aar…® akubhusura, zimbusur Č …®z…®nd…® z…®kagwa k Čnz…®ra, ibhinyunyi bh…®kaaza, bh…®kazirya.  
