\v 17 N…®rabhabh Č Čr…®ra amaheene, abhar Č Čt…®r…®ri na abhaat Č bhe eheene bhaaru, bhaar…® bhariigomba korora gan Č mokorora, nawe bhatagar Č Čz…®, na kwigwa gan Č mukwigwa, nawe bhataagiigwir…®. 
\s1 Y…®…®su aragar Čra ekerenjo chu umubhusuri 
