\v 3 Heroode akagambabhu, k Č k Čbha ewe newe aar…® agwatir…® Yoohana. Akamobhoha mokebhoho, ig Čr Č wa amang ľana gu ubhukw…®ri bhwa Heroode na H…®r Č Čdiya. H…®r Č Čdiya wuyo, aar…®  Čm Čkari wa Firip Č, umwabh Č.  
\v 4 Kereeta ndeewa char…®, Yoohana akabh Č Čr…®ra Heroode, ‚ÄúNi‚ÄĎmugir Č kukw…®ra  Čm Čkari wa umwabh Č.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 14:4 \xt Rora Abharaawi 18:16, 20:21.\f* 
\v 5 Heroode aar…® aramohya …®nz…®ra yu ukwita Yoohana, nawe aar…® ar Č Čbhaha abhaat Č k Č k Čbha bhiisiriiry…® Yoohana k Čbha n…®‚ÄĎm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri wa Mungu. 
