\s1 Y…®…®su arahorya abharw…®r…® bha Genezar…®ti 
\r (Maaroko 6:53‚ÄĎ56) 
\p  
\v 34 Han Č Y…®…®su na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhaambukir…® …®nyanza, bhakahika muchar Č cha Genezar…®ti.  
\v 35 Han Č abhaat Č bha ahagero hayo bh Č Čbh Č Črir…® n…®‚ÄĎY…®…®su, bhakat Čma abhaat Č k Čragan ľya amang ľana gaaz…® m Čz…®…®s…® z Č Čsi za haguh…®. Bhakamoreetera abharw…®r…® bhaabh Č bh Č Čsi.  
\v 36 Bhakam Čsabha abhiisiririry…® abharw…®r…® bhakun ľy…® naabha ripind Č rye engebho yaaz…®. Bh Č Čsi bhan Č bhaamukuniry…®ku, bhakahora amarw…®r…® gaabh Č. 
\c 15  
\s1 Y…®…®su araanga isim Čka ya abhak Čr Č 
\r (Maaroko 7:1‚ÄĎ13) 
\p  
\v 1 Neho Abhafarisaayo na abhiija bhi imigir Č ja Musa obhorebhe bhakarwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu bhakaaza kwa Y…®…®su, bhakamubhuurya,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúKwak…® abh…®…®ga bhaaz Č bhatigir…® isim Čka y…®n Č abhakaruka bh…®…®t Č bhaatutigiir…®? Bhararya ibhyakurya, …®n Č bhatiisaabhir…® amabhoko gaabh Č ch…®mbu ikwenderwa!‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 15:2 \fk Bhatiisaabhir…® amabhoko gaabh Č ch…®mbu ikwenderwa\ft , enzobhooro yaku ubhwisaabhi bhwar…® sim Čka y…® ∆ók…®yaahudi. Abhayaahudi bhakarora ni mugir Č kutiga amanar Č gan Č.\f* 
\p  
\v 3 Akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúNdora imw…® mutigir…® imigir Č ja Mungu, kwa kutuna zisim Čka zaanyu?  
\v 4 Mungu abhugir…®, ‚Äė…Ąs Č Čk…® wuus Č na onyoko,‚Äô\f + \fr 15:4a \xt Rora K Čh Čr Čka 20:12; Amahiity Č gi Imigir Č 5:16.\f* naatu akabhuga, ‚ÄėW Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č ak Čt Čka wiis…® hamw…® unina, areenderwa akw…®.‚Äô\f + \fr 15:4b \xt Rora K Čh Čr Čka 21:17; Abharaawi 20:9.\f* 
\v 5 Nawe imw…® m Čhaabhuga,  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č araabh Č Čr…®r…® wiis…® hamw…® unina, ‚ÄėEbhegero bh…®n Č nangaturir…® k Čk Čsakirya, nihuruchiry…® kwa Mungu ikimweso,‚Äô  
\v 6 ang Č  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo atakwenderwa k Čs Č Čka wiis…® hamw…® unina. Nawe kuyo nekwe okorega …®ng ľana ya Mungu ig Čr Č wu kutuna zisim Čka zaanyu.  
\v 7 Abhabh…®…®hi imw…®, Mungu akagamba amaheene ig Čr Č waanyu k Čh…®t…®ra k Čm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri Isaaya ch…®mbu yandikirw…® k Čbha, 
\q1  
\v 8 ‚ÄėAbhaat Č bhan Č bhahaans Č Čka kwa mang ľana ageene, 
\q1 nawe zekoro zaabh Č zere kore na niiny…®. 
\q1  
\v 9 Okosengera kwabh Č k Čtaana bhwera, 
\q1 k Č k Čbha bhariija amiija ga abhaat Č 
\q1 kina n…®‚ÄĎga Mungu.‚Äô\f + \fr 15:9 \xt Rora Isaaya 29:13.\f*‚Ää‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Amabh…® g Č Čsi gararwa mozekoro 
\r (Maaroko 7:14‚ÄĎ23) 
\p  
\v 10 Mmbe, Y…®…®su akabh…®r…®k…®ra riribhita rya abhaat Č, akabhabh Č Čr…®ra,  
\v 11 ‚ÄúMwitegeerere bhwaheene, na mwobhoore! ∆ótar…® k…®n Č kikusik…®ra mumunywa necho kekokora  Čm Č Čt Č kobhenga.\f + \fr 15:11 \fk Kobhenga\ft . K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora ring ľana \ft \+it  Čbh Čbh…®ngi\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* Nawe, amang ľana gan Č gakurwa mumunywa, nego gakugirya  Čm Č Čt Č abhenge.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 12 Neho abh…®…®ga bhakamujaku, bhakamubhuurya, ‚Äú…Ąm…®nyir…® k Čbha han Č Abhafarisaayo bhiigwir…® amang ľana garya bhakiigatana bh Čk Čng ľu?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 13 Akagarukirya, ‚Äú∆óbh…®t Č Čt Č bhy Čsi bh…®n Č bh…®taahambirw…® na Bhaabha wa mwisaar Č, bhiriihwa.  
\v 14 M Čbhatig…®! Bhayo n…®‚ÄĎbhakangati abhah Čku bhan Č bhahaakangata abhah Čku. …Ąm Čh Čku ar…®…®kangat…®  Čm Čh Čku  Čm Čk…®ndichaz…®, bh Č Čsi bharagwa mwir Č Čma.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 15 Peetero akabhuga, ‚ÄúT Čgar Čr…®r…® ekerenjo kiyo.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 16 Y…®…®su akam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúNa niimw…® m Čk…®…®r…® komenya?  
\v 17 M Čt…®…®z…® k Čbha ch Čch Čsi k…®n Č kikusik…®ra mumunywa, k…®haaja m Čnda, ak Čmara k…®haahuruchibhwa ig Čt Č w Č  Čm Čbh…®r…®?  
\v 18 Nawe gan Č gakurwa mumunywa, gararwa mokoro yaaz…®, nego gakugirya abhenge.  
\v 19 Mokoro y Č  Čm Č Čt Č n…®mu gahaarwa amiis…®…®gi amabh…®, ubhwiti,  Čbh Čs…®bh…®…®ti, …®taar Č, ubhwibhi,  Čr Čr…®m…® na amatuki.  
\v 20 G Č Čsi gayo, nego gahaakora  Čm Č Čt Č abhenge. Nawe kurya utiisaabhir…® amabhoko ch…®mbu ikwenderwa k Čtakugirya obhenge.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Ubhwisirirya bhw Č  Čm Čkari w Čn Č atar…® …Ąm Čyaahudi 
\r (Maaroko 7:24‚ÄĎ30) 
\p  
\v 21 Mmbe, Y…®…®su akabh Č Čka harya, akaja  Čr Čbhaara rwa z…®mb…®ri za Tiiro na Sid Č Čni.  
\v 22 Neho akarumana n Č  Čm Čkari w Čmw…®, aar…® M Čkanaani. …Ąm Čkari wuyo akaja kwawe aragamba kwiraka, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č, Umwana w Č  Čm Čt…®mi Daudi, ondorere …®bh…®g Čngi! Umuucha waan…® ana risambwa r…®ram Čnyaacha bh Čk Čng ľu.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 23 Nawe atam Čgarukiiry…® ing ľana ry Čry Čsi. Neho, abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhakamujaku na k Čm Čsabha bharabhuga, ‚ÄúMutig…® aj…®, k Č k Čbha ang ľ…®hir…® k Čt Čr…®g…®s…®ra …®n Č araturwa inyuma.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Akagarukirya, ‚ÄúNitumirw…® ig Čr Č wa Abhiizira…®ri, bhaang…® z…®ng ľ Čndu z…®n Č zibhurir…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 25 …Ąm Čkari wuyo akiisuka kwa Y…®…®su, akahigama m Čbh Čtang…® bhwaz…®, akabhuga, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č, nsakirya!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 26 Akam Čgarukirya, ‚Äú∆ótar…® bhwaheene kogega ibhyakurya bhya abhaana na k Čtaashirya zimbwa.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 15:26 \fk Kogega ibhyakurya bhya abhaana na k Čtaashirya zimbwa\ft , enzobhooro y Č  Čbh Čgambi bh Čn Č n…®‚ÄĎk Čbha, Abhayaahudi bhabhone  Čbh Čsakirya hinga abhaat Č bhan Č bhatar…® Abhayaahudi bhak…®…®r…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 27 …Ąm Čkari wuyo akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®mbu …®r…® …Ąm Čk Čr Č, nawe n Č Čr Č zimbwa z Č Čsi z…®haatoora amasaaj Č gan Č gakotorobhoka haas…® kurwa kwigari rya abhak Čr Č bhaabh Č.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28 Y…®…®su akam Čgarukirya, ‚Äú…Ąm Čkari w Čn Č, ubhwisirirya bhwaz Č, n…®‚ÄĎbh Čk Čr Č! Ekorwe kwa naaw…® ch…®mbu ukwenda.‚ÄĚ Hayohayo, umuucha waaz…® akahora. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arahorya abharw…®r…® bhaaru 
\p  
\v 29 Y…®…®su akabh Č Čka hayo, akah…®ta rusiz Č w…® …®nyanza ya Gariraaya. Akatiira k Čk…®g Čr Č, akiikara iyo.  
\v 30 Abhaat Č bhaaru bhakamujaku, bhakamoreetera amagata, abhah Čku, abharema, amamuumu na abharw…®r…® abhand…® bhaaru, bhakabhat Č Čra haguh…® na amag Čr Č gaaz…®, akabhahorya.  
\v 31 Abhaat Č bhakar Čg Č Čra bh Čk Čng ľu han Č bhaar Č Čz…® amamuumu garagamba, abharema bharahora, amagata garagenda na abhah Čku bhararora. Bhakag Čnga Mungu wa Izira…®ri. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arariisha abhaat Č bh…®kw…® bhene na bh Čsaag Č 
\r (Maaroko 8:1‚ÄĎ10) 
\p  
\v 32 Y…®…®su akabhabh…®r…®k…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®rabharorera …®bh…®g Čngi abhaat Č bhan Č, k Č k Čbha twik…®…®r…® nabh Č zisik Č isat Č, nangw…®n Č bhataana ibhyakurya. N…®takwenda n…®bharag…® bhaj…® m Čz…®mb…®ri zaabh Č bhan…® …®nzara, k Č k Čbha abhand…® bharat Čra kugwa ubhwesa.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 33 Abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhakamubhuurya, ‚ÄúNang Č, turi mwit…®r…®g Č, na abhaat Č, n…®‚ÄĎbhaaru. T Črat Čra kobhona hayi …®m…®kaat…® ju ukwisa kubhiigutya bh Č Čsi?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 34 Y…®…®su akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúM Čn…® …®m…®kaat…® …®r…®nga?‚ÄĚ 
\p Bhakam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúT Čnaj Č muhungat…® ni ibhisw…® bhisuuhubhu.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 35 Mmbe, Y…®…®su akaswaja abhaat Č bhiikar…® haas…®.  
\v 36 Akagega …®m…®kaat…® muhungat…® na ziisw…® zirya akabh Č Čr…®ra Mungu, az Čmiry…®. Ak Čmara akasunyura, akabhaha abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, bhakasondya abhaat Č.  
\v 37 Abhaat Č bh Č Čsi bhakarya, bhakiig Čta. Ak Čmara abh…®…®ga bhakabhiringa amasaaj Č, bhakiizurya …®bh…®h Č Čz Č muhungat…®.  
\v 38 Abhaat Č bhan Č bhaariir…® bhaar…® abhasubh…® bh…®kw…® bhene, kuruushaku abhakari na abhaana.  
\v 39 Ak Čmara Y…®…®su akaraga abhaat Č bhayo, akasik…®ra mubhwat Č, akaja  Čr Čbhaara rwa Magadaani. 
\c 16  
\s1 Abhaat Č bhareenda ich…®r…®k…®n ľy Č 
\r (Maaroko 8:11‚ÄĎ13; Ruuka 12:54‚ÄĎ56) 
\p  
\v 1 Ak Čmara Abhafarisaayo na Abhasadukaayo bhakaja kwa Y…®…®su komogema. Bhakam Čsabha akore ich…®r…®k…®n ľy Č kwerecha k Čbha aaruur…® kwa Mungu.  
\v 2 Y…®…®su akabhagarukirya, [‚ÄúHan Č ikuhika ubhutik Č, imw…® m Črabhuga, ‚ÄėTabh Č Čri amasaar Č garabha bhwaheene, k Č k Čbha risaar Č rere kore zenzota z…®bhanzir…®.‚Äô  
\v 3 Na ritabh Č Čri m Črabhuga, ‚ÄėReero …®ratweka imbura y Č  Čm Čkama, k Č k Čbha risaar Č irabhuru na amasaar Č gabhuukir…®.‚Äô Kan…®, mw…®z…® kwobhoora ibhy…®r…®k…®n ľy Č bhya amasaar Č, nawe m Čtak Čt Čra kwobhoora ibhy…®r…®k…®n ľy Č bhya ribhaga r…®n Č!]  
\v 4 Imw…® urwibh Čr Č  Čr Čbh…® na r Čn Č r Čtar…® oroheene! Moreenda ich…®r…®k…®n ľy Č, nawe m Čtakwerechwa ich…®r…®k…®n ľy Č ch Čch Čsi, kuruushaku k…®mw…® k…®n Č chang…® ch Č  Čm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri Yoona.‚ÄĚ Neho Y…®…®su akarwa hayo, akabhatiga. 
\s1 Amiija amabh…® ga Abhafarisaayo na Abhasadukaayo 
\r (Maaroko 8:14‚ÄĎ21) 
\p  
\v 5 Mmbe, abh…®…®ga bha Y…®…®su bhakaamb Čka …®nyanza, nawe bhaar…® bh…®…®bhir…® kogega …®m…®kaat…®.  
\v 6 Y…®…®su akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúMwiyangar…®r…® nu ubhutunduuru bhwa Abhafarisaayo na Abhasadukaayo.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 7 Abh…®…®ga bhakatanga k Čgambana abheene kobheene, bharabhuga, ‚ÄúArabhugabhu, k Č k Čbha t Čtaag…®gir…® …®m…®kaat…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 8 Y…®…®su akamenya g Č Čsi gan Č bhaar…® bhak Čgambana, akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúImw…® abhaat Č bhu ubhwisirirya ubhusuuhu! Kwak…® muriimonyerera k Čbha m Čtaana …®m…®kaat…®?  
\v 9 Kuhika nang Č, m Čk…®…®r…® komenya? M Čtakuhiita ch…®mbu abhaat Č bh…®kw…® bh…®taan Č bhiigutir…® kwa m…®kaat…® …®taan Č girya? Mukiizurya …®bh…®h Č Čz Č bh…®r…®nga bhya amasaaj Č?  
\v 10 Hamw…® m Čtakuhiita …®m…®kaat…® muhungat…® girya, k Čbhaat Č bh…®kw…® bhene? Mukiizurya …®bh…®h Č Čz Č bh…®r…®nga bhya amasaaj Č?  
\v 11 Ndora m Čtakwobhoora gan Č nagambir…®, …®tar…® ig Čr Č w…® …®m…®kaat…®? Mmbe, n…®rabhuga, mwiyangar…®r…® nu ubhutunduuru bhwa Abhafarisaayo na Abhasadukaayo.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Neho, abh…®…®ga bh Č Čbh Č Črir…® k Čbha ataar…® aragamba ig Čr Č wu kwiyangar…®ra nu ubhutunduuru bhwo okokora …®m…®kaat…®, nawe ig Čr Č wa amiija g Č  Čr Čr…®m…® rwa Abhafarisaayo na Abhasadukaayo. 
\s1 Peetero ariisirirya k Čbha Y…®…®su newe Kiriisit Č 
\r (Maaroko 8:27‚ÄĎ30; Ruuka 9:18‚ÄĎ21) 
\p  
\v 13 Han Č Y…®…®su aahikir…®  Čr Čbhaara rwa Kaisaariya‚ÄĎFiripi, akabhabhuurya abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, ‚ÄúAbhaat Č bharabhuga, Umwana w Č …Ąm Č Čt Č n…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…®?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 14 Bhakam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúAbhand…® bharabhuga, naaw…® Yoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi, abhand…® bharabhuga aw…®, n…®‚ÄĎ∆ó…®riya na abhand…® bharabhuga aw…®, n…®‚ÄĎY…®r…®miya hamw…® n…®‚ÄĎw Čmw…® waho wa abhar Č Čt…®r…®ri bha Mungu abhand…® bh…® …®kar…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 15 Y…®…®su akabhabhuurya, ‚ÄúNa niimw…® m Črabhuga iny…®, n…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…®?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 16 Sim Č Čni Peetero akam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúAw…®, ni‚ÄĎKiriisit Č,\f + \fr 16:16 \fk Kiriisit Č\ft , enzobhooro yaku n…®‚ÄĎMasiya.\f* Umwana wa Mungu w Č  Čbh Čh Čru.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 17 Y…®…®su akabhuga, ‚ÄúHak…®r…®ku aw…® Sim Č Čni umwana wa Yoona,  Čhakirw…®, k Č k Čbha atareeho  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č akuhumburiir…® amaheene gan Č, nawe n…®‚ÄĎBhaabha wa mwisaar Č.  
\v 18 Iny…® n…®rak Čbh Č Čr…®ra, aw…® Peetero,\f + \fr 16:18 \fk Peetero\ft , enzobhooro yaku ni‚ÄĎritar…®.\f* aw…® ni‚ÄĎritar…®, ni ig Čr Č wa ritar…® r…®n Č, n…®r Č Čmbaka risengerero ryan…®, na zinguru zu uruku z…®takurihiza.  
\v 19 Iny…® n…®rakoha zihunguru z Č  Čbh Čt…®mi bhwa mwisaar Č. Amang ľana g Č Čsi gan Č  Čk Čbha waangir…® k Č Čs…®, garabha gaangirw…® mwisaar Č. Na gan Č uriisiriry…® k Č Čs…®, garabha giisiririibhw…® mwisaar Č.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 16:19 \xt Rora Mataayo 18:18.\f* 
\v 20 Neho akabhahama abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® k Čbha, bhatabh Č Čr…®ra  Čm Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi k Čbha ewe newe Kiriisit Č. 
\s1 Y…®…®su aragamba ig Čr Č wu ukukwa nu ukury Čka kwaz…® 
\r (Maaroko 8:31‚Äď9:1; Ruuka 9:22‚ÄĎ27) 
\p  
\v 21 K Čtang…®ra ribhaga riyo, Y…®…®su akatanga k Črag…®r…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® habhw…®r Č k Čbha areenderwa aj…® Y…®rusar…®…®mu, na anyaakibhw…® bh Čk Čng ľu. Akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, aranyaakibhwa na abhakaruka bha Abhayaahudi, na abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani na abhiija bhi imigir Č ja Musa, kuhika kwitwa. Nawe urusik Č rwa katat Č kw…®ma ukukwa kwaz…®, arary Čka.  
\v 22 Neho Peetero akamuhira Y…®…®su rusiz Č, akatanga komorecha arabhuga, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č, Mungu agahity…® gayo kore! Gataaza kokobhona!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 23 Nawe Y…®…®su akiich Čra, akabh Č Čr…®ra Peetero, ‚ÄúSh…®taani, nuurw…® inyuma waan…®! …Ąragema kundibh…®ra kokora ch…®mbu Mungu akwenda! Amiis…®…®gi gaaz Č gatar…® ga Mungu, nawe ga abhaat Č.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Mmbe, Y…®…®su akabh Č Čr…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, ‚Äú…Ąm Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi w Čn Č areende kuntuna, areenderwa iyang…® umwene, agege  Čm Čsarabha gwaz…®,\f + \fr 16:24 \fk Agege  Čm Čsarabha gwaz…®\ft , enzobhooro yaku ni‚ÄĎkwisirirya Y…®…®su n Č Čr Č kukwa ig Čr Č waaz…®.\f* antun…®.  
