\v 12 N…®rabhabh Č Čr…®ra k Čbha ∆ó…®riya\f + \fr 17:12 \ft Y…®…®su arar…®ng ľaan ľya \fk ∆ó…®riya \ft na Yoohana …Ąm Čbhatiizi. Yoohana akakorera Y…®…®su …®nz…®ra, emeremo g…®n Č Abhayaahudi bhaar…® bhariisega k Čbha ∆ó…®riya arakora. \xt Rora Mataayo 11:13‚ÄĎ14.\f* amarir…® kuuza, nawe abhaat Č bhataam Čm…®nyir…®, bh Č Čsi bhakamokorera amabh…® g Č Čsi gan Č bh…®…®ndir…®. ∆óbhu…®bhu nu Umwana w Č …Ąm Č Čt Č, aranyaakibhwa m Čmabhoko gaabh Č.‚ÄĚ  
