\v 21 Neho Peetero akaaza kwa Y…®…®su, akamubhuurya, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č, ar…®…®bh…® umwisirirya  Čm Čk…®ndichan…® ansaririiry…®, nereenderwa nemobheerere manga kar…®nga? Manga muhungat…®?‚ÄĚ 
