\v 22 Y…®…®su akam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúN…®k Čbh Č Čr…®r…®, …®tar…® manga muhungat…®bhu, nawe omobheerere  Čm Čk…®ndichaz Č muhungat…® manga merongo muhungat…®.\f + \fr 18:22 \fk Muhungat…® manga merongo muhungat…®\ft , enzobhooro yaku, umwabh…®r…® ribhaga ry Čsi.\f* 
