\v 12 Y…®…®su akasik…®ra mwihekaaru. Akaheebhera ig Čt Č abhaat Č bhan Č bhaar…® bhakugurya na k Čg Čra ebhegero. Akabharing Čra zemeeza za bhan Č bhaar…® bhak Čk…®ran ľya zimpirya ni ibhitumb…® bhya bhan Č bhaar…® bhakugurya ibhiguuti.  
\v 13 Akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúYandikirw…® m ČMaand…®k Č Amar…®ndu, ‚ÄėInyumba yaan…® …®rabha inyumba ya amasabhi.‚Äô\f + \fr 21:13a \xt Rora Isaaya 56:7.\f* Nawe imw…® m Čy…®k Črir…® k Čbha ribhigi rya abhasaakuri.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 21:13b \xt Rora Y…®r…®miya 7:11.\f* 
