\v 8 ‚ÄúAk Čmara  Čm Čt…®mi wuyo akabh Č Čr…®ra bhamb Č Čsa bhaaz…®, ‚ÄėEbhegero bhy Čsi bhyu ubhuryakari bh…®marir…® kokorwa, nawe abharaarikwa bhataar…® bhareenderwa kuuza.  
\v 9 Mmbe nang Č, muj…® k Čnz…®ra ya amah Čkana, m Čbh Č Čr…®r…® bh Čbh Č Čsi bhan Č mukurumana nabh Č, bhaaz…® kubhuryakari.‚Äô  
\v 10 Bhamb Č Čsa bhayo bhakaja k Čnz…®ra, bhakagar Čka na abhaat Č bhan Č bhaabhar Č Čz…®, abhabh…® na abhaz Čmu. Bhakasik…®ra mwibhuru ryu ubhuryakari kuhika rikiiz Čra. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúNawe han Č  Čm Čt…®mi aasikiir…® mwibhuru ryi isigukuru korereke arore abhagini, akarora  Čm Č Čt Č w Čmw…® w Čn Č atiibh Čhir…® engebho yu ubhuryakari.  
\v 12 Akamubhuurya, ‚ÄėM Čsaani waan…®,  Čkasik…®rabhw…® m Čn Č, …®n Č utiibh Čhir…® engebho yu ubhuryakari?‚Äô Nawe  Čm Č Čt Č wuyo akakira.  
\v 13 Mmbe,  Čm Čt…®mi akabh Č Čr…®ra abhahocha bhaaz…®, ‚ÄėMomobhohe amag Čr Č na amabhoko, morekere ig Čt Č mukiirimya. Iyo bharar…®ra na kokepeha.‚Äô‚Ää‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 14 Y…®…®su akamariirya kwa k Čgamba, ‚ÄúAbhaat Č bhan Č bhakubhirikirwa kusik…®ra m Čbh Čt…®mi bhwa mwisaar Č, n…®‚ÄĎbhaaru, nawe bhan Č bhar Čbhw…®rw…® kusik…®ra, n…®‚ÄĎbhasuuhu.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhuuribhwa ig Čr Č w Č  Čk Čr…®ha rig Č Čti 
