\p  
\v 34 Han Č Abhafarisaayo bhiigwir…® k Čbha Y…®…®su aar…® ahizir…® Abhasadukaayo k Čbh Čgambi bhwaz…®, bhakiibhiringa hamw…®mw…®.  
