\v 38 Riswaja r…®n Č neryo rik Čr Č k Čk…®ra amaswaja agand…® g Č Čsi, naatu nego ganu ubhw…®ndi k Čk…®ra g Č Čsi.  
\v 39 Ubhuswaja bhwa kabh…®r…® bhutuubh…®…®n…® na bhuyo, nabhw…® bh Črabhuga, ‚Äė…Ąm Čs…®…®g…® nyar Čbh…®ri waaz Č ch…®mbu wis…®…®gir…® aumwene.‚Äô\f + \fr 22:39 \xt Rora Abharaawi 19:18.\f* 
\v 40 Imigir Č j Čsi ja Musa na amiija ga abhar Č Čt…®r…®ri bhiriisega amaswaja abh…®r…® gayo.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhuurya Abhafarisaayo ig Čr Č wa Kiriisit Č 
