\p Bhakam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúAreenderwa iitw…®!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 67 Ak Čmara, bhakamutw…®ra amat…® mubhush Č, bhakamotema ibhikundi. Abhand…® bhakamotema amag Č Čhu,  
\v 68 na k Čm Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúAw…® Kiriisit Č, orootorere, n…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…® w Čn Č ak Čt…®mir…®?‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Peetero araanga Y…®…®su 
\r (Maaroko 14:66‚ÄĎ72; Ruuka 22:56‚ÄĎ62; Yoohana 18:15‚ÄĎ18, 25‚ÄĎ27) 
\p  
\v 69 Mmbe, ribhaga riyoriyo, Peetero aar…® iik…®…®r…® ig Čt Č mukisik Č hayo. Neho omohocha w Čmw…® w…® …®k…®kari akamujaku, akam Čbh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúNa naaw…® waar…® hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su wa Gariraaya.‚ÄĚ 
