\v 20 Nawe abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani na abhakaruka bha Abhayaahudi bhakakorokomba abhaat Č bhasabh…® Piraato abhataz Čr…®r…® Bharaabha na k Čt…®n…®ra Y…®…®su korereke iitw…®. 
\p  
\v 21 Piraato akabhabhuurya naatu, ‚ÄúN…®‚ÄĎw…®…®w…® w Čn Č mukwenda n…®bhataz Čr…®r…® gat…® wa abhabhohwa bhabh…®r…® bhan Č?‚ÄĚ 
\p Bhakam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúBharaabha!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 22 Piraato akabhabhuurya naatu, ‚ÄúMmbe nekorebhw…® Y…®…®su w Čn Č akubhirikirwa Kiriisit Č?‚ÄĚ 
\p Abhaat Č bh Č Čsi bhakar…®g…®sa bharabhuga, ‚ÄúM Čm Čbhamb…® k Čm Čsarabha!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 23 Piraato akabhabhuurya naatu, ‚ÄúAsariry…®k…®?‚ÄĚ 
\p Nawe ebho bhakoongera k Čr…®g…®sa bharabhuga, ‚ÄúM Čm Čbhamb…® k Čm Čsarabha!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Han Č Piraato  Čbh Č Črir…® k Čbha atak Čt Čra kuch Čra amiis…®…®gi ga abhaat Č bharya na k Čbha bhatangir…® rir…®g…®, akagega amanzi na kwisaabha amabhoko gaaz…® m Čbh Čtang…® bhwabh Č. Akakorabhu kwerecha k Čbha ataana isoro ry Čry Čsi. Neho akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúIny…® n…®taana bh Čbh…® bhw Čbhw Čsi ku uruku rw Č  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č we eheene. Ring ľana r…®n Č ni‚ÄĎg Čr Č waanyu imubheene!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 25 Abhaat Č bh Č Čsi bhakam Čgarukirya, ‚ÄúRisaah…® ryu uruku rwa Y…®…®su r…®bh…® ig Čr Č w…®…®t Č na abhaana bh…®…®t Č!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 26 Ak Čmara Piraato akataz Čra Bharaabha, na akaswaja abhasirikar…® korereke bhateme Y…®…®su …®m…®zariti na k Čm Čbhamba k Čm Čsarabha. 
\s1 Abhasirikar…® bharasiihya Y…®…®su 
\r (Maaroko 15:16‚ÄĎ20; Yoohana 19:2‚ÄĎ3) 
\p  
\v 27 Neho abhasirikar…® bhu umwanangwa wi Ikiruumi bhakagega Y…®…®su, bhakaja nawe mwik Čr Č ryu umwanangwa. Bhakabhiringa riribhita ik Čr Č rya abhasirikar…®, bhakamwiruguura.  
\v 28 Bhakamuruusha zengebho zaaz…®, bhakamwibhohya …®kanz Č imbiriiri.  
\v 29 Bhakagisa …®k…®r Čng Č cha amahwa, bhakamwibhohya kumutw…® na rik Čr…® kokobhoko kwaz…® ku ubhury Č korereke arorekan…® nch Č  Čm Čt…®mi. Bhakahigama m Čbh Čtang…® bhwaz…®, ak Čmara bhakatanga komorega bharabhuga, ‚ÄúMorembe,  Čm Čt…®mi wa Abhayaahudi!‚ÄĚ  
\v 30 Ak Čmara bhakamutw…®ra amat…®, bhakagega rik Čr…® rirya bhakamotema nary Č kumutw…®.  
\v 31 Han Č abhasirikar…® bhayo bhaamarir…® kumusiihya, bhakamuruusha …®kanz Č yirya na kumwibhohya zengebho zaaz…®. Ak Čmara, bhakaja nawe k Čm Čbhamba k Čm Čsarabha. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhambwa k Čm Čsarabha 
\r (Maaroko 15:21‚ÄĎ32; Ruuka 23:26‚ÄĎ43; Yoohana 19:17‚ÄĎ27) 
\p  
\v 32 Han Č bhaar…® bhararwa m Čr Čbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu, bhakabhona  Čm Č Čt Č w Čmw…® Mukireene, w Čn Č akubhirikirwa Sim Č Čni. Abhasirikar…® bhayo bhakam Čhat…®ka kogega  Čm Čsarabha gwa Y…®…®su.  
\v 33 Ak Čmara, bhakahika ahagero han Č haabhirikiirw…® G Črig Č Čta, enzobhooro yaku n…®‚ÄĎk ČK…®hanga chu Umutw…®.  
\v 34 Bhakaha Y…®…®su idivaayi y…®n Č bhaar…® bhasangiry…® n…® …®nd Čr Č.\f + \fr 27:34 \xt Rora Zabhuri 69:21.\f* Nawe han Č aabh Čnjiry…®, akaanga kunywa.  
\v 35 Bhakam Čbhamba k Čm Čsarabha, ak Čmara bhakatwana zengebho zaaz…® kwa kokora ubhwit Č Čri. [Neho r…®kabha ring ľana r…®n Č ryagambirw…® n Č  Čm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri ig Čr Č wa Y…®…®su k Čbha ‚ÄúBhakatwana zengebho zaan…® na bhakakora ubhwit Č Čri ig Čr Č wa amiibhoho gaan…®.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 27:35 \xt Rora Zabhuri 22:18.\f*]  
\v 36 Bhakiikara hayo korereke bhamuriibh…®.  
\v 37 Bhakat Č Čra  Čr Čbhao ig Čr Č wu umutw…® gwaz…®. …Ąr Čbhao ruyo rwar…® rwandikirw…® amang ľana g Č  Čk Čm Čgamba k Čbha, ‚Äú\sc W Čn Č n…®‚ÄĎY…®…®su, …Ąm Čt…®mi wa Abhayaahudi\sc*.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 38 Ahagero hayo, bhaareho abhasaakuri bhabh…®r…®, bhakabhambwa hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su,  Čw Čmw…®  Čr Čbhaara rwu ubhury Č n Č  Čw Čnd…®  Čr Čbhaara rw Č  Čbh Čm Čsi.\fig Y…®…®su k Čm Čsarabha|alt="Yesu msalabani" src="CN01836C.TIF" size="col" loc="MAT 27:38" copy="¬© 1996 David C Cook. Used by permission." ref="27:38" \fig* 
\v 39 Abhaat Č bhan Č bhaar…® bhak Čh…®ta k Čnz…®ra hayo, bhakam Čt Čka, bharasingisha imitw…® jabh Č bharabhuga,  
\v 40 ‚ÄúNang Č,  Čtar…® naaw…® wabhugir…®  Čraasha rihekaaru rya Mungu na kury Čmbaka kwa sik Č isat Č? Nang Č, ar…®…®bh…® aw…® ni‚ÄĎMwana wa Mungu, wiituury…® aumwene, wiik…® k Čm Čsarabha!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 41 ∆óbhu…®bhu, abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani, abhiija bhi imigir Č ja Musa hamw…®mw…® na abhakaruka bha Abhayaahudi bhakamorega bharabhuga, ‚ÄúAkasabh Čra abhand…®, nawe atak Čt Čra kwisabh Čra umwene!  
\v 42 Ar…®…®bh…® n…®‚ÄĎm Čt…®mi wa Abhiizira…®ri, mmbe iik…® k Čm Čsarabha, neho na niitw…® tukumwisirirya.  
\v 43 Ewe aramwisega Mungu, na abhugir…®, ‚ÄėIny…® ni‚ÄĎMwana wa Mungu.‚Äô Mmbe, nang Č ar…®…®bh…® heene Mungu am Čs…®…®gir…®, am Čsabh Čr…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 44 Abhasaakuri bhan Č bhaabhambirw…® hamw…®mw…® nawe, bh Č Čsi bhakam Čt Čka. 
\s1 Uruku rwa Y…®…®su 
\r (Maaroko 15:33‚ÄĎ41; Ruuka 23:44‚ÄĎ49; Yoohana 19:28‚ÄĎ30) 
\p  
\v 45 Mmbe, kw…®ma ribhaga rya z…®…®sa isaasabha umwise kuhika z…®…®sa kenda, …®kabha ikiirimya kuchar Č ch Čsi.  
\v 46 Z…®…®sa kenda, Y…®…®su akar…®ra kwiraka ik Čr Č arabhuga, ‚Äú∆ór Č Čyi, ∆ór Č Čyi! Raama sabhakitaani?‚ÄĚ Enzobhooro yaku, ‚ÄúMungu waan…®, Mungu waan…®! Ndora untigir…®?‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 27:46 \xt Rora Zabhuri 22:1.\f* 
\p  
\v 47 Han Č abhaat Č bhan Č bhaar…® hayo bhiigwir…® amang ľana gayo, abhand…® bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúW Čn Č arabh…®r…®k…®ra ∆ó…®riya  Čm Čr Č Čt…®r…®ri wa Mungu.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 27:47 \ft ∆ó…®riya aragambwa han Č k Č k Čbha Abhayaahudi bhaaru bhaar…® bhariisirirya k Čbha ∆ó…®riya atakuur…®, nawe Mungu akamogega k Č Čs…® han Č m Čh Čru na kuja nawe mwisaar Č. Na bhaar…® bhariisega k Čbha ∆ó…®riya aragar Čka kwik…® k Č Čs…®. \xt Rora 2 Abhat…®mi 2:11; Maraaki 4:5.\f* 
\p  
\v 48 Hayohayo, w Čmw…® waabh Č akaryara mwega, akagega ripuupya, akakorya m Čmarwa amar Čr Č gi idivaayi, akat Č Čra ripuupya kwik Čr…®, akamoha Y…®…®su anyw…®.  
\v 49 Nawe abhand…® bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúTiga torore ar…®…®bh…® ∆ó…®riya araaza k Čm Čsabh Čra!‚ÄĚ  
\v 50 Neho Y…®…®su akar…®ra kwik…® kwiraka ik Čr Č, akatin ľya. 
\p  
\v 51 Hayohayo, ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru\f + \fr 27:51 \fk Ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru \ft riyo ryar…® mwihekaaru, r…®rak…®nga abhaat Č bhatasik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu, han Č ubhw…®r Č bhwa Mungu bhwik…®…®r…®. \xt Rora Abh…®…®bhuraaniya 6:19, 10:19‚ÄĎ22. \ft K Čmarag…®r…®ra bh Čk Čng ľu, rora ring ľana \ft \+it rihekaaru\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* r…®kabhaar Čka mbaara ibh…®r…® kurwa ig Čr Č kuhika iyaas…®. ∆ó…®s…® …®karigita, zikurungutar…® z…®kabhaar Čka.  
\v 52 Zimbih…®ra zikiig Čka n…® …®m…®bh…®r…® myaru ja abhar…®ndu bha Mungu g…®kary Čka.  
\v 53 Han Č Y…®…®su aaryukir…® bhakarwa muzimbih…®ra zaabh Č, bhakasik…®ra Y…®rusar…®…®mu, bhakarorwa na abhaat Č bhaaru. 
\p  
\v 54 Han Č  Čm Čk Čr Č wa abhasirikar…® hamw…®mw…® na bhan Č bhaar…® bhakuriibha Y…®…®su bhaar Č Čz…® ikirigit Č ch…® …®…®s…® na agand…® g Č Čsi gan Č gak Čriibhw…®, bhak Č Čbhaha bh Čk Čng ľu, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúHeene,  Čm Č Čt Č w Čn Č aar…® Umwana wa Mungu!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 55 Hayo bhaareho na abhakari bhaaru bhan Č bhaar…® bhakutuna Y…®…®su kurwa Gariraaya na komohokerya. Abhakari bhayo bhiimiiriir…® kwa kore bhararora g Č Čsi gan Č gaar…® gakokorebhwa.  
\v 56 M Čbhakari bhayo, bhaar…®mu Mariyamu wa Magidarena, Mariyamu unina Yaakobho na Yuusufu, na unina wa abhaana bha Zebhedaayo. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhiikwa 
\r (Maaroko 15:42‚ÄĎ47; Ruuka 23:50‚ÄĎ56; Yoohana 19:38‚ÄĎ42) 
\p  
\v 57 Han Č ryahikir…® rigoroobha, akaaza umw…®ga w Čmw…® wa Y…®…®su iriina ryaz…® Yuusufu. Yuusufu wuyo aar…® muniibhi kurwa  Čr Čbh…®ri rwa Arimataaya.  
\v 58 Yuusufu akaja kwa Piraato, akam Čsabha …®k…®t Čnd Č cha Y…®…®su. Piraato akaswaja abhasirikar…® bhaaz…® bhamohe …®k…®t Čnd Č kiyo.  
\v 59 Akaja, akagega …®k…®t Čnd Č, akakiring…®ra m Čsanda.  
\v 60 Akat Č Čra …®k…®t Čnd Č mumbih…®ra yaaz…® iihya ya ribhigi r…®n Č ryar…® ritukirw…® kwitar…®. Ak Čmara akahiringitya riibhw…® ik Čr Č akakundikirya ikisik Č chi imbih…®ra, akarweho.  
\v 61 Ribhaga riyo, Mariyamu wa Magidarena na Mariyamu  Čw Čnd…® wurya, bhaar…® bhiik…®…®r…® bh…®…®r…®k…®…®r…® imbih…®ra. 
\s1 Abhasirikar…® bharariibha imbih…®ra 
\p  
\v 62 Urusik Č rwa kabh…®r…®, r Čn Č rwar…® urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čt Č Čr Č, abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani na Abhafarisaayo bhakiibhiringa kwa Piraato.  
\v 63 Bhakabh Č Čr…®ra Piraato, ‚Äú…Ąm Čk Čr Č, t Črahiita k Čbha han Č  Čm Čbh…®…®hi wurya aar…® ak…®…®r…® m Čh Čru, akabhuga, ‚ÄėUrusik Č rwa katat Č, n…®rary Čka.‚Äô  
\v 64 Nang Č t Črasabha  Čbhat Čm…® abhasirikar…® bhariibh…® imbih…®ra kuhika urusik Č rwa katat Č. Ar…®…®bh…®  Čtak Čt Č Čra abhariibhi, abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bharat Čra bhakaaza kwibha …®k…®t Čnd Č chaz…® na k Čkangirirya abhaat Č k Čbha aryukir…® kurwa m Čbhaku. Bharaakorebhu,  Čr Čr…®m…® ruyo r Črabha r Čbh…® bh Čk Čng ľu k Čk…®ra r Čn Č rwakangatir…®.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 65 Piraato akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúMogege abhasirikar…®, muj…® muriibh…® kwa amanaga gaanyu g Č Čsi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 66 Neho bhakaja kumbih…®ra, bhakat Č Čra  Čr Čkaam Č kwibhw…®, korereke rihiringitibhw…®, bhamenye. Bhakabhatiga abhasirikar…® hayo korereke bhariibh…® imbih…®ra. 
\c 28  
\s1 Y…®…®su arary Čka 
\r (Maaroko 16:1‚ÄĎ10; Ruuka 24:1‚ÄĎ12; Yoohana 20:1‚ÄĎ10) 
\p  
\v 1 Han Č urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čt Č Čr Č rwahitir…®, m Čmacha urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čtang…® rwi inyuma,\f + \fr 28:1 \fk Urusik Č rw Č  Čbh Čtang…® rwi inyuma \ft k ČBhayaahudi ni‚ÄĎJumapiri.\f* Mariyamu wa Magidarena hamw…®mw…® na Mariyamu  Čw Čnd…® wurya, bhakaja korora imbih…®ra. 
\p  
\v 2 Rogendo r Čmw…®, k…®kabhaho ikirigit Č k…®k Čr Č ch…® …®…®s…®, k Č k Čbha maraika w Č …Ąm Čk Čr Č Mungu akiika kurwa mwisaar Č. Maraika wuyo akiisuka kumbih…®ra, akahiringitya riibhw…® rirya rusiz Č, akaryikar…®ra.  
\v 3 Aar…® arabharya nch Č  Čr Čk Čbha, na zengebho zaaz…® zaar…® nz…®r Č pee ncho omosoke.  
\v 4 Han Č abhasirikar…® bharya bhaar Č Čz…® gayo, bhak Č Čbhaha bh Čk Čng ľu, bhakabha nkina bhakuur…®. 
\p  
\v 5 Hayo, maraika wuyo akabh Č Čr…®ra abhakari bharya, ‚ÄúM Čt Č Čbhaha! N…®…®z…® m Čramohya Y…®…®su wa Nazar…®…®ti, w Čn Č aabhambirw…®.  
\v 6 Atar…® han Č! Aryukir…®, ch…®mbu aabhugir…®. Muuz…® morore han Č bhaar…® bham Čt…®…®r…®.  
\v 7 Muj…® bhwang Č, m Čbhabh Č Čr…®r…® abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, ‚ÄėAryukir…® kurwa k Čbhaku, na arabhakangat…®ra kuja muchar Č cha Gariraaya. Iyo n…®yu mokomobhona!‚Äô Nang Č n…®marir…® k Čbhabh Č Čr…®ra k…®n Č char…® k…®nd…®…®tir…®!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 8 Neho abhakari bhayo bhakabh Č Čka bhwang Č kurwa mumbih…®ra hayo, bhanu ubhw Čbha no obhozomerwa bh Čk Čr Č. Bhakaryara kuja k Čbhabh Č Čr…®ra abh…®…®ga gan Č maraika aabhabhuuriir…®.  
\v 9 Mmbe, han Č bhaar…® bharaja, Y…®…®su akarumana nabh Č, akabhakeerya, ‚ÄúMorembe!‚ÄĚ Bhakamwisuk…®ra, bhakamugwata amag Čr Č gaaz…®, bhakamosengera.  
\v 10 Neho Y…®…®su akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúM Čt Č Čbhaha. Muj…® m Čbhabh Č Čr…®r…® abhahiiri bhaan…®\f + \fr 28:10 \fk Abhahiiri bhaan…®\ft , enzobhooro yaku n…®‚ÄĎbh…®…®ga bhaaz…®.\f* bhaj…® Gariraaya, iyo n…®yu bharaambone.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Abhariibhi bhi imbih…®ra ya Y…®…®su bharagamba  Čr Čr…®m…® 
\p  
\v 11 Han Č abhakari bhayo bhaar…® bhakuja, abhasirikar…® obhorebhe abhariibhi bhi imbih…®ra ya Y…®…®su bhakaja m Čr Čbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu. Han Č bhaahikir…®, bhakarag…®r…®ra abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani g Č Čsi gan Č gaak Čriibhw…®. 
\p  
\v 12 Ak Čmara abhak Čr Č bha abhakuhaani bhayo bhakarumana na abhakaruka bha Abhayaahudi, bhakagambana na kuhitya k Čbhaha abhasirikar…® bhary…® amasooya ga zimpirya nzaru.  
\v 13 Bhakabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚Äú…Ąm Č Čt Č w Čw Č Čsi araabhabhuury…® ig Čr Č wa gan Č gak Črirw…®, mubhug…®, ‚ÄėUbhutik Č twar…® tuhindiir…® zendooro, abh…®…®ga bhakaaza bhakamwibha.‚Äô  
\v 14 Han Č Piraato ariigw…® gayo, itw…® t Čragambana nawe korereke m Čtaaza kusik…®ra m Čnyaak Č.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Mmbe abhasirikar…® bhakagega zimpirya na bhakakora ch…®mbu bhaabhuuriirw…® na abhak Čr Č bha Abhayaahudi. Amang ľana gaabh Č g Č  Čr Čr…®m…® gakanyaragana bh Čk Čng ľu gat…® wa Abhayaahudi kuhika reero y…®n Č. 
\s1 Amaswaja g…® …®t…®n…®r Č ya Y…®…®su k Čbh…®…®ga bhaaz…® 
\r (Maaroko 16:14‚ÄĎ18; Ruuka 24:36‚ÄĎ49; Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 1:6‚ÄĎ9) 
\p  
\v 16 Abh…®…®ga bha Y…®…®su ikumi na w Čmw…® bhakaja Gariraaya m Čk…®g Čr Č k…®n Č Y…®…®su aabh…®…®r…®kiry…®.  
\v 17 Han Č bhaam Čr Č Čz…®, bhakamosengera, nangabha abhand…® bhaar…® na amak…®bhw…® k Čbha n…®‚ÄĎY…®…®su.  
\v 18 Y…®…®su akabhiisuk…®ra, akabhabh Č Čr…®ra, ‚ÄúN…®h…®…®rw…®  Čbh Čnaja bhw Čsi bhwa mwisaar Č na m Č Čs…®.  
\v 19 Nang Č muj…® k Čbhaat Č bhi ibhyar Č bhy Čsi na k Čbhakora k Čbha abh…®…®ga bhaan…®. M Čbhabhatiiz…® kuriina rya Bhaabha, na ryu Umwana na rye Ekoro ∆ónd…®ndu.  
\v 20 Mubhiij…® kugwata g Č Čsi gan Č nabhaswajiry…® imw…®. Rora, na niiny…® n…®r…® hamw…®mw…® na niimw…® ribhaga ry Čsi, kuhika m Čt…®n…®r Č y…® …®…®s…®.‚ÄĚ